text: Mississippi Highway 46 (MS 46) is a state highway located in the U.S. State of Mississippi. The western terminus of the route is at the western terminus of MS 782 in Mantee in Webster County and the eastern terminus is at MS 50 west of West Point in Clay County. Along the way, MS 47 intersects MS 15 in Mantee and then the Natchez Trace Parkway east of Mantee. ==Major intersections== ==References== 046 Category:Transportation in Clay County, Mississippi Category:Transportation in Webster County, Mississippi
title: Mississippi Highway 46
